data.description: Price Reduction! Home is sold strictly As IS! No repairs will be made by the seller!   Nestled in the heart of Suitland, Maryland, this inviting semi-detached home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this residence is an urban oasis with a private driveway for off-street parking, ensuring a hassle-free lifestyle.  Step into a recently renovated kitchen, where modern finishes and thoughtful design come together seamlessly. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply love to entertain, this space is sure to impress. Beyond the kitchen, discover the warmth of a well-designed interior, with ample natural light gracing each room.  The charm extends outdoors with a backyard retreat, creating a perfect spot for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee or hosting barbecues in this delightful space.  Situated just minutes from the metro, this home provides unparalleled accessibility to the bustling energy of downtown DC and the connectivity of the 495 beltway. Embrace the convenience of nearby shops, making daily errands a breeze.  In the vibrant city of Suitland, this property stands out as a testament to modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to call this meticulously maintained residence your own. Take the next step towards a lifestyle of comfort, connectivity, and community. Your dream home awaits!
